        <mxCell id="p2-fan-note" parent="p2-fanout" style="text;html=1;fontSize=10;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#C925D1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=6;whiteSpace=wrap;" value="&lt;b&gt;Pattern:&lt;/b&gt; non-interactive consumers receive PUSH via DDB Stream — not SSE.&lt;br&gt;Filter milestone/error events only; suppress verbose text triads.&lt;br&gt;Slack bots MUST ack in 3s → this path gives async delivery after submission.&lt;br&gt;Rate-limiting prevents spam on chatty agents (per-session throttle)." vertex="1">
